Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:25.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:31.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:49.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:54.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:04.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:14.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:25.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:30.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:34.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:44.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Former Squad 5 Captain, Sosuke Aizen,\NFormer Squad 3 Captain, Gin Ichimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and former Squad 9 Captain,\NKaname Tosen…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:01.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The whereabouts of these three\Nare still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, according to the report
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:06.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from the Department of Research\N& Development,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:11.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Hogyoku in Aizen’s possession\Nrequires much preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:15.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and a good amount of time\Nto utilize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, in my judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it will be quite a while\Nbefore it can be misused.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, those three still\Npose a great threat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:29.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the Soul Society and\Nto the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:34.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have therefore organized\Nan Investigation Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and mobilized them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:40.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is all for today.\NYou are dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, they’ve organized\Nan Investigation Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he calls them\Nan Investigation Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but they’re just assassins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen’s in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:59.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess he asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that Renji…\NI hear he’s been assigned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the town where\Nthat Ryoka boy comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Seems he’s been keeping busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it’s just that I heard\Nsome disturbing rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,about that the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:44.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… We searched all night\Nand got nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:47.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… I don’t sense Inoue’s\NSpiritual Pressure anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only we knew\Nwhat that thing was…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of looked like\Nthe Gate of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there’s no way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hell would make off\Nwith a living human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Renji…\NWhy are you here at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! I’m in charge of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:22.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If something strange happens,\Nit’s my duty to do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, the point of your argument\Nis slightly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:30.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were asked what\Nyou were doing here at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I off, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, the question was…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NThis isn’t getting us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers me most\Nis what happened earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tatsuki…\NIsn’t Inoue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Inoue…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that? A new student?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NOrihime…Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no one here\Nby that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their memory of Inoue\Nhas been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like when\NRukia disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone went to the trouble\Nof using the “Memory Replacement.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:19.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means they’re taking\Nour actions seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:24.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue hasn’t simply disappeared.\NSomeone’s behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then let’s go and\Ncheck out her apartment again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able\Nto find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.\NCome on. Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about your classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be worrying\Nabout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to break down\Nthe door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.\NLet me handle this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…isn’t that illegal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no other way, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it might be better\Nthan breaking down the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make sure\Nno one sees me from the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, you’re really good\Nat detailed jobs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit making me sound worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What’s it like in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:43.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there isn’t anything good…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t get much\Nto eat last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are two cups…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What, and no cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to keep\Ntalking about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:10.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m hungry!\NIt hurts my stomach when you yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you just ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn’t enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:18.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What in the world\Nare you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This means…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the being that possessed the Spiritual\NPressure we sensed late last night
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was invited into this room\Nby Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:29.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It really was a strange\NSpiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means Inoue\Nknew who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s cell phone is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my Soul Pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s not. It’s a call…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!\NYou’re crowding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got your friend.\NShe’s with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:06.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm… What should I do?\NShould I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d you kidnap Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t go into people’s houses\Nwithout permission, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I’ll call the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were we being watched?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I want to see her.\NBring her back, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t we play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If you boys win,\NI might return your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…! You think you’re funny…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let her get to you! Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:53.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the park at 2-chome\Nwithin three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re even one second late,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no telling what\Nwill happen to your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within three minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what’s what,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but we have no choice\Nbut to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You’d better be safe, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, don’t you have\Nany idea who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She called you on\Nyour Soul Pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This was just supplied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody could find out\Nthe number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We haven’t got much time.\NLet’s hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:27.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:28.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you got a little faster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the short time\Nwe didn’t see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just got slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Kurosaki!\NPeople will think you’re strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You look weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there’s no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We got here in three minutes!\NShow yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The first hurdle… You passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The first hurdle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!\NWe got here in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give Inoue back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! This is a game!\NIt’s no fun if it ends so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kid…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the supermarket in\N the 3-chome shopping arcade…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,within three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! That’s a crazy distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe your friend will die…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Get outta the way, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The 2nd hurdle, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else answered the phone,\Nso you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that in the rules?\NYou didn’t tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your friend’s gonna die.\NSo long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:21.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. There’s no use\Nin your getting excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fooled you! Shall we go\N to your third hurdle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you…\NMaking fools of us…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, Inoue’s safety comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:56.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Inoue all right?\NLet me hear her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let you hear her voice\Nif you pass the third hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Hurry up and tell me what it is.\NWhere now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.93,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara's Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your phone!\NWhere’s your phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, what are you all\Nso excited about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our phone is inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! We’re going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the big hurry, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Freeloader, it’s not time\Nfor lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How did you know\Nthis number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you calling from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you tell where it's coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since you passed the 3rd hurdle…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, trace the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only the police can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll give you a bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make a recording of the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:13.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eight o’clock tonight…\Ntry going back to her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may find her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why tonight?\NBring her back now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…\NDon’t get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! At least let me hear her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don’t hang up!\NHello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How noisy!\NWhat in the world’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don’t get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! At least let me hear her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a kidnapping,\Ndoesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anyone\Nwho would do this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would just hand Inoue over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s some sort of trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the fact\Nthat she called this shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’d say she’s not\Nan ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There just isn’t enough information\Nto be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Yoruichi.\NThere’s too little to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there any way you can check,\NMr. Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I’ll have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the first case\Nlike this for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,8:00 tonight…\NAre you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!\NWe can’t leave Inoue to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,8:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:40.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you going too, Jinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's just,\Nif they’re going at 8:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,our freeloader won’t\Nneed dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anything going on inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, you didn’t bring your cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh,\NI sent it to the cleaners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You send it to the cleaners?\NThat thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? It’s 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Inoue’s apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It’s locked again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I’ll open it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:39.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no time for that!\NChad! Break it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:39.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really bring you back to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were kidnapped last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:06.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think hard, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the last thing\Nthat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…? Let’s see, today…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:20.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a new semester,\Nso I went back to school…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,met up with everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:26.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I ate shaved ice with Tatsuki\Nand got a headache…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I went home\Nand after eating dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,went right to bed, I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The new semester started yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They got to her and\Nerased her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, I’m glad you’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we can’t breathe easily yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.\NLet’s keep an eye out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:52.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try going back to her apartment.\NYou may find her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…\NDon’t get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. I sent it through\Nthe voice analyzer, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this voice has no Reimon,\NSpirit Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No Reimon, Spirit Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That would be equivalent to\Na voice print in a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I’ve never seen\Na cloud like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Menos…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. It differs somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing’s happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! It’s not safe near\Nthe windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The door won’t open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You… You’re not Inoue!\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:49.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Just shake her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t use your zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They may just be\Nusing her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:22.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!\NYou’re not the one who called us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or course, not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would be weird if I had\Na voice like that, wouldn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kurodo.\NAnd here’s someone else…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, Noba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:00.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s that kid! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who\Nphoned us, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am! My name is Lirin.\NNice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a game! A game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She has some nerve…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hard fighting a kid…\NI’ll take the guy on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take the guy with the hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! You take care of the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no good, I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:15.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:25.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:40.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:42.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:48.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:23:07.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:17.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:27.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:55.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something wrong\Nwith my gigai, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:57.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just can’t get out of it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:23:59.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall I lend you\Nmy Soul Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:03.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thanks! That’d be great!\NLet’s see, yours was…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:05.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, did you want something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my mind.\NI think I might get stupid…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:19.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:21.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make a sound…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:41.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:24:48.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.26,0:24:54.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!